sentences: Lee Doo-hyun (Hangul: 이두현; born 1980), better known by his stage name Ra.
D (Hangul: 라디) is a South Korean singer, songwriter and producer who debuted in 2002 with the album My Name is Ra.
After a 6-year hiatus, he made a comeback in February 2013 with the single "It's Been So Long".
On October 26, 2015, he announced RealCollabo would be closed after established for seven years.
